notification-daemon: The Desktop Notifications framework
notification-daemon:
notification-daemon: The Desktop Notifications framework provides a standard
notification-daemon: way of doing passive pop-up notifications on the
notification-daemon: Linux desktop. These are designed to notify the user
notification-daemon: of something without interrupting their work with a
notification-daemon: dialog box that they must close. Passive popups can
notification-daemon: automatically disappear after a short period of time.
